 for 12 years<\\/p>\",\"myBlockUrl\":\"Health\",\"tags\":[\"34\"],\"coloroption\":\"blue\",\"rowNumber\":\"row1\"}},\"26\":{\"type\":\"multipleBlocks\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockImage\":[\"76\"],\"myBlockHeading\":\"Youth Work\",\"myBlockTextboxText\":\"<p>Liz Dean Consultancy has teamed up with Laura Clark, a very experienced Sex Educator to advocate for the sex and relationship rights of people with learning disabilities<\\/p>\",\"myBlockUrl\":\"youthwork\",\"tags\":[\"81\"],\"coloroption\":\"blue\",\"rowNumber\":\"row2\"}},\"28\":{\"type\":\"multipleBlocks\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"myBlockImage\":[\"62\"],\"myBlockHeading\":\"Relationships\",\"myBlockTextboxText\":\"<p>I have recently been working on behalf of the Brighton & Hove Healthy Schools Team and I have developed a teaching pack covering the impact and influence of the media and pornography on young people\'s sexualisation<\\/p>\",\"myBlockUrl\":\"Relationships\",\"tags\":[\"32\"],\"coloroption\":\"red\",\"rowNumber\":\"row2\"}}}}}', '2016-05-10 19:35:03', '2016-05-10 19:35:03', 'c79077ba-3b7b-4393-80ac-5edbf468ae0e'),
